{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 44 "II-1.  (10 points) Analyz
e the graph of     " }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {XPPEDIT 19 1 "f := (1
0*x^2-10*x-60)/(2*x^3-4*x^2+x-2);" "6#>%\"fG*&,(*&\"#5\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"
